names of the officers, don't look at the title, look at the people all these people are great guys and drop everything at a moments notice to come help even for little problems.  I may not be the most liked officer simply because I am a little hard edged on raids and I appologise for hurt feelings but basicaly I hate having people die on raids other than me and If I see people doing stuff that will get themselves kill or others then I yell otherwise its just battle comands that are to be followed so we can win.<br>
<br>
